rsocket: Handle TCP_MAXSEG socket option

netperf uses the TCP_MAXSEG socket option.  Add support for it.
Problem reported by Sridhar Samudrala <sri@us.ibm.com>

Signed-off-by: Sean Hefty <sean.hefty@intel.com>


---

